  ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ 
  -->

<ext_description linkend="Information_rights_arm.Information_usage_right_relationship">
This records the relationship of one <b>Information_usage_right</b> to another.
<example> Where one <b>Information_usage_right</b> supercedes another, then the original right is pointed to by the <b>relating</b>
attribute, its replacement by the <b>related</b> attribute, and the <b>role</b> attribute takes the value "supercedes".</example>
</ext_description>


